# Changelog Updates

After completing any code changes in this project, update `CHANGELOG.md` with a new entry.

## Entry format

```markdown
### YYYY-MM-DD — Name
**Short description of what changed**

- Files created/modified with brief explanation
- Why the change was made
- Key decisions or tradeoffs noted

---
```

## Rules

- Add new entries at the top of the `## Log` section (reverse chronological order)
- Include: date, who, what files changed, why, and any notable decisions
- Keep entries concise but complete enough for someone catching up
- Group related changes into a single entry per session
- Always end an entry with `---` separator
